thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by ANNE

author: ANNE
title: ANNE
text: I was making a complicated rental across a range of locations and decided to ring the company rather than try to complete my request on-line. My experience was very good and everything was as discussed when I picked up the car. I found the Redspot staff very friendly and helpful on all occasions
